OL,3,CArrests made after pedestrian killed
OL,4,Cin collision with car
OL,6,FA man in his forties has died and two
OL,7,Fpeople have been arrested on suspicion
OL,8,Fof murder after reports of a
OL,9,Fpedestrian being hit by a car near
OL,10,FBarnsley.
OL,12,FPolice say they were called to Rose
OL,13,FTree Avenue in Cudworth at around
OL,14,F4.55pm on Friday 3 April by the
OL,15,Fambulance service following a report
OL,16,Fof a collision between a 45-year-old
OL,17,Fman and a white Volkswagen Tourag.
OL,19,FThe man died at the scene. His family
OL,20,Fhas been informed and are being
OL,21,Fsupported by officers.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
