OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1775653862
OL,3,CArrests made after pedestrian killed
OL,4,Cin collision with car
OL,6,FA 60-year-old man and a 38-year-old
OL,7,Fwoman have been arrested on suspicion
OL,8,Fof murder and remain in police custody.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Simon
OL,11,FCartwright said: "Our investigation
OL,12,Finto this tragic incident is still in
OL,13,Fits early stages and our thoughts
OL,14,Ffirst and foremost are with the
OL,15,Fvictim's family, friends and loved
OL,16,Fones.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
